<h2>
	Alt Text
</h2>

<p>
	When adding an image, you should also add '<strong>Alternative Text</strong>' to help with your sites accessibility. To do this, you need to double click on the asset which will open a popup to the side of your screen.
</p>

<p>
	Here you will see an <strong>Alt Text</strong> field which you can fill in with a description of each image.
</p>

